## Goal

Nick's consulting-pivot narrative is consistent, compelling, and active across all channels (resume, LinkedIn, cover letters, interview answers). BCG TDA prep is complete and case-ready. All Tranche 1 and Tranche 2 applications are submitted with correct, reviewed artefacts. The story reads: engineer to strategic digital consultant, with engineering as the differentiator, not the departure point.

Done is measured by: BCG TDA application advancing (case interview invite or explicit feedback), Tranche 1 applications submitted, active pipeline of at least three live opportunities, and a story bank mapped to common consulting competencies.

